lead_paragraph: Wicketkeeper Parthiv Patel has retained his place in the India side for the fourth test against England after Wriddhiman Saha failed to recover from a thigh strain, the team said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Wicketkeeper Patel Retained for Fourth Test Against England
